Use of chat or OOC: 1 gossip point
Use of atalk: 5 gossip points
Use of gossip: 10 gossip points
Use of shout: 500 gossip points

Avatars (AVs) and Immortals (Imms) can also dock your gossip points for
inappropriate use of chat channels.  The following are the suggested
guidelines but are not necessarily guaranteed:

Using the wrong channel (using atalk for chat, etc): warning
     After a warning, 25 points may be docked
Minor swearing on a public chat channel: 50 gossip points
Major swearing of use of derogatory terms (in a non-in-game manner):
     100 gossip points
Doing the same on a more permanent forum (notes, titles, etc) will double
     the docked amount.  Docking may occur multiple times until the offensive
     material has been removed.

Abusiveness to AVs or Imms doing their job may result in loss of all gossip
