logging alternate characters on.  In addition, players may not log in and out
frequently in order to speed up area resets.  This also includes constant
voiding in areas.
   
@B@b*@n Each account may have only one character on at a time, and playing
multiple characters via multiple accounts is also not permitted.  This rule
extends to equipment trading and the 5-minute rule as well...  even if you've
cleverly managed to create multiple accounts, characters in all your accounts
are subject to these rules, as if they were all under the same account.
  
