"phule's standards for objects:

non magical objects should all be level 1.

if an object deviates strongly from the standard, it is probably magical
(magically-thin or very lightweight plate armor with better AC than
heavy, thick, iron plate, for instance).

so this help file tries to lay out the 'level 1' standards for objects,
as well as how objects deviate from level 1 as they deviate from the
standard non-magical base.

